78.7	Salvation	Salvation	Salvation, in religion, is the saving of the soul, that is, its deliverance from sin and its consequences. It may also be called "deliverance" or "redemption" from sin and its effects.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/The_Creation_of_Adam.jpg/120px-The_Creation_of_Adam.jpg
